ayer; he has excellent people skills as well as excellent business acumen. I would not hesitate to work together with him again.", "recommendations/0/name": "Michel D. LAVERGNE", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "Retired Hotelier", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/mdlavergne/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABPqqcB5bZLLkfPfTRKCupBp-OE15AAR40", "recommendations/1/context": "Chitra worked with Rod  on the same team", "recommendations/1/date": "June 5, 2012", "recommendations/1/description": "I had the pleasure working with Rod Santos at the Metro Inn opening team and I found Rod to be one of the most competent Chief Engineers, a great team player and he is very knowledgeable in his work. Given the opportunity I would not hestitae to work with him again.", "recommendations/1/name": "Rod  D.", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "M.IEAust. PEng. MEP, PMP, M. AIRAH,M.ASHRAE, CHFE,CEM,CLSSBB, JP", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/rodsantos28/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAJvpTgBr2wmZKWvS4SZaWhBHCEUB_EkTSw", "recommendations/2/context": "Chitra worked with Rod  on the same team", "recommendations/2/date": "May 20, 2012", "recommendations/2/description": "I had the pleasure working with Rod Santos during my tenure at the Furama Hotel Sydney. I found Rod to be a very knowledgeable, reliable, and efficient Chief Engineer. His analytical and open minded approach to new challenges and his diplomatic way of handling situation are especially commendable. He is definitely one of the best chief engineers that I have worked with. Given the opportunity I would not hesitate to work with him again.", "recommendations/2/name": "Rod  D.", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "M.IEAust. PEng. MEP, PMP, M. AIRAH,M.ASHRAE, CHFE,CEM,CLSSBB, JP", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/rodsantos28/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAJvpTgBr2wmZKWvS4SZaWhBHCEUB_EkTSw", "recommendations/3/context": "Chitra reported directly to Thierry", "recommendations/3/date": "May 18, 2012", "recommendations/3/description": "I had the pleasure working with Mr Thierry Douin at the Intercontinental Hotel Phonm Penh during its preopening. He poses an in-depth knowledge about all aspects of hotel management and shares his knowledge freely with his subordinates mentoring and motivating them. He is result oriented, focused on exceptional service and guest satisfaction. He has a remarkable capacity to bring out the best in his staff.  I have no doubt Mr. Douin is the most effective General Manager I have ever worked with.", "recommendations/3/name": "Thierry Douin", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "Retired Global Luxury Hotelier, Mentor, Travelling and hiking photographer.", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/thierrydouin/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAUMwD8Ba5sqOjzo-tYuFMVM3_1mgUm56ec", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Tony managed Chitra directly", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "November 14, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "Chitra has an excellent eye for detail and works well in a team environment.", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Tony Mathers", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "Business Broker at Raine & Horne Commercial Dee Why", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/tony-mathers-81868837/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAfAupQBf_v5F88rFz16LvU2HKOzEFIdrFM", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "TIM worked with Chitra on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "June 14, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "Chitra and I worked together for the pre-opening and opening of what is now the Holiday Inn Darling Harbour.\nChitra was an integral member of the executive team and was highly organized and efficient both in the set up and the subsequent operation of her department. She was well liked by her team and the other department heads and in no small measure contributed to the success of this very busy and profitable property.\nIt is great to see her ongoing success in everything she has attempted in her career subsequently, which has doubtless been well deserved…", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "TIM JOHNS", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "Hospitality recruiter for leading and luxury hotels - specialist in hotel recruitment", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/timjohns/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAGwaLoBVpHQqApFNj3PXlgM3RdebH9QuRE", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Michel D. was Chitra's client", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "June 13, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "Chitra was contracted as FO Manager during the pre-opening and soft opening phase of the Sunway Hotel in PNH. She did a great Job at grooming the Front Office Team and preparing the Local Front Office Manager to head up this division. I am sure she has done well in her field of work since1998...", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Michel D. LAVERGNE", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Retired Hotelier", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/mdlavergne/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABPqqcB5bZLLkfPfTRKCupBp-OE15AAR40", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Rod  worked with Chitra on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "June 5, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "Chitra and I worked together during the pre-opening of then Metro Inn Hotel Sydney a 288 rooms 4.5 Star Hotel at Darling Harbour corner China Town. Chitra is a hard working Executive Housekeeper and a very knowledgeable one, we are the first Group of Hotel Executive that managed to beat the accommodation level in China Town and Darling Harbour at 97% average all 7 days Week and on weekends at 100%, the dedication of all executive specially Chitra keeping our guest rooms, and public area very competitive by maintaining it clean environment and very supportive staff with a happy smiles. No wonder why when Furama Hotel International kept our team during the rebranding in 1994 at Darling Harbour and 1996 at Albion Street Sydney. If I will be given the opportunity to run my own Hotel or Captain a Chain of Hotel, I know the Group of Executive who will I choose to run and operate it and one cream of the crop will always be Chitra Chandrasiri, the Lady with a million dollar smiles.", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Rod  D.", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "M.IEAust. PEng. MEP, PMP, M. AIRAH,M.ASHRAE, CHFE,CEM,CLSSBB, JP", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/rodsantos28/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAJvpTgBr2wmZKWvS4SZaWhBHCEUB_EkTSw", "recommendationsReceived/4/context": "Thierry managed Chitra directly", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "May 19, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "For the opening of the first 5 star international hotel in Cambodia, the InterContinental Phnom Penh, I was very fortunate to have Chitra heading the training department. This was a key position for the hotel as all the labour force available was totally unskilled. Chitra did a marvellous job in instilling the right attitude and mindset in the local employees thanks to her  natural warmth, humility and patience. She truly cares for people and was well appreciated by everyone. I would not hesitate to employ her again should she be available.", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "Thierry Douin", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "Retired Global Luxury Hotelier, Mentor, Travelling and hiking photographer.", "recommendationsReceived/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/thierrydouin/", "recommendationsReceived/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAUMwD8Ba5sqOjzo-tYuFMVM3_1mgUm56ec", "skills/0/title": "Property Management", "skills/1/title": "Hotel Booking", "skills/2/title": "Concept Development", "skills/3/tit